name: Beta Fish B / Pez betta B
description:
From the Imaginary Fish series.
As a teenager I had a betta fish. I was surprised that when I got to my room he approached the glass to see me. And I saw him back. And I fed him/her.

De la serie Peces imaginarios.
De adolescente tenía un pez betta. Me sorprendía que al llegar a mi cuarto él se acercaba al vidrio para verme. Y yo le veía de vuelta. Y le daba de comer.
